Description: ==================
        Investment Tracker
        ==================
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/investment_tracker.svg
                :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/investment_tracker
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/com/rankoliang/investment_tracker.svg
